## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of sources reviewed. Some sources may not reflect the most current economic conditions or policy changes. Additionally, the analysis is based on available literature and may not capture all perspectives or potential unintended consequences of increased state support. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the long-term impacts of such interventions.